---

<section id="who-its-for" class="testimonials-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Who It's For</h2>
      <p>ContentGlowz is for people who have something to say but not enough time to say it everywhere</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Solo Founders</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">🚀</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">You're building a product and need to ship content for SEO, social, and newsletters. But writing isn't your job. ContentGlowz turns your weekly ritual into drafts you can review.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Content Creators</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">✍️</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">You have one idea. ContentGlowz helps shape it into the formats you need: a blog post, a social post, a newsletter section, or a short video script.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>SEO-Driven Sites</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">📈</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">DataForSEO-powered keyword research feeds the pipeline. Articles target real search volume, and SERP tracking shows what is working after publication.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Affiliate Marketers</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">💰</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">Register your affiliate programs. ContentGlowz surfaces matching opportunities and keeps active, paused, and expired programs visible before links are used.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Small Agencies</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">🏢</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">Manage multiple projects with separate personas, voices, and publishing channels. The Pro plan gives unlimited projects. Scale content for all your clients from one dashboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Mobile-First Creators</h3>
          <div class="use-case-icon card-title-icon">📱</div>
        </div>
        <p class="quote">Review content from your phone on the train. Approve, skip, or edit from a mobile-first review flow designed for thumbs, not keyboards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .section-header p {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-light-gray);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: background var(--duration-slow), box-shadow var(--duration-slow), transform var(--duration-slow);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    background: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .testimonial-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .testimonial-card .card-title-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
  }

  .quote {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-section {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
</style>
